---
title: Pesto Roasted Vegetable Fusilli with Rocket-Pear Salad & Parmesan
description: Up the ante on pasta night with this supercharged bowl of flavour. From the veggies, which are roasted and then tossed with basil pesto, to the tomato sauce infused with garlic and chilli, this is destined for greatness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pesto-roasted-vegetable-fusilli-72467b5c.jpg
